OL,3,CAmbulance driver who caused death of
OL,4,Cparamedic by careless driving avoids
OL,5,Cjail
OL,7,FAn ambulance driver who crashed,
OL,8,Fkilling a young paramedic, has
OL,9,Freceived a suspended jail sentence
OL,10,Fafter pleading guilty to causing death
OL,11,Fby careless driving.
OL,13,FNewly qualified paramedic Alice Clark,
OL,14,Fwas on board the South East Coast
OL,15,Fambulance being driven by Edward
OL,16,FRiding when it collided with a lorry
OL,17,Fnear Tonbridge in 2022.
OL,19,FEdward Riding from Crowborough was
OL,20,Fsaid to be driving the vehicle to an
OL,21,Femergency with blue lights.
