OL,7,FAlice Clark's family say that she was
OL,8,Fso excited to have qualified as a
OL,9,Fparamedic that she looked forward to
OL,10,Fevery shift.
OL,12,FBut two months into her new job, the
OL,13,F21-year-old was killed while
OL,14,Fresponding to a 999 call.
OL,16,FAlice was a passenger in an ambulance
OL,17,Fwhich collided with a cement lorry on
OL,18,Fthe A21 near Tonbridge on a January
OL,19,Fnight in 2022.
