OL,7,FThe driver of the ambulance, Edward
OL,8,FRiding, 45, admitted causing Alice's
OL,9,Fdeath by careless driving.
OL,11,FMaidstone Crown Court heard Riding was
OL,12,Fdriving at over 80mph when he mistook
OL,13,Fa lay-by for the exit that he needed.
OL,15,FThe ambulance hit a kerb, struck one
OL,16,Fparked lorry, then hit the rear of
OL,17,Fanother.
