OL,7,FAlice Clark suffered catastrophic
OL,8,Finjuries and died at the scene. Riding
OL,9,Fwas airlifted to hospital with
OL,10,Fmultiple injuries, while another
OL,11,Fstudent paramedic who was in the back
OL,12,Fof the ambulance was also seriously
OL,13,Fhurt.
OL,15,FAt the funeral of Alice Clark,
OL,16,Fparamedics formed a guard of honour as
OL,17,Fthe hearse arrived at the Garden of
OL,18,FEngland crematorium near Sittingbourne.
