OL,7,FHer former colleagues spoke of their
OL,8,Fprofound sense of loss after her
OL,9,Ftragic death.
OL,11,FThe prosecution told the court that
OL,12,FEdward Riding had a reputation for
OL,13,Fdriving fast and showing off behind
OL,14,Fthe wheel.
OL,16,FOn one occasion, he said he wanted to
OL,17,Fturn a student paramedic as green as
OL,18,Fher uniform.
