OL,7,FThe judge told Riding that on the
OL,8,Fnight in question, he'd made a
OL,9,Fterrible mistake through inattention.
OL,11,FThe paramedic was given a suspended
OL,12,Fprison sentence of nine months.
OL,14,FAlice Clark's father told the court
OL,15,Fthat her 'brilliant life had been cut
OL,16,Ffar too short by a careless act that
OL,17,Fcould and should have been avoided.'
OL,19,FHe said her death had a devastating
OL,20,Fimpact on her family and they found it
OL,21,Fhard to comprehend that she was gone.
