OL,7,FA South East Coast Ambulance Service
OL,8,F(SECAmb) spokesperson said: "Our
OL,9,Fthoughts are with Alice's family and
OL,10,Feveryone affected by this tragic
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,F"We welcome the conclusion of the
OL,14,Fcourt case but understand that is a
OL,15,Fvery difficult time for all those
OL,16,Faffected.
OL,18,F"We will ensure support is available
OL,19,Fto any colleagues who require it."
